<i>noun</i>: 횡포 [횡포/휑포], 학정 [학쩡], 폭정 [폭쩡], 포학 [포ː학], 독재 [독째] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>횡포 [횡포/휑포]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; despotism</dd><br>
<dd>제멋대로 굴며 매우 난폭함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of acting as one pleases and being extremely violent.</dd><br>
<dt>학정 [학쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; dictatorship; despotism</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 모질고 잔인한 정치.</dd><br>
<dd>An extremely heartless and cruel rule by a king, government, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>폭정 [폭쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; dictatorship; despotism</dd><br>
<dd>매우 사납고 악한 정치.</dd><br>
<dd>An extremely heartless and cruel rule by a king, government, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>포학 [포ː학]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; atrocity</dd><br>
<dd>성질이나 행동이 몹시 잔인하고 난폭함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one’s personality or behavior being very cruel and fierce.</dd><br>
<dt>독재 [독째]</dt><br>
<dd>1. dictatorship; tyranny</dd><br>
<dd>특정한 개인이나 집단이 모든 권력을 차지하고 마음대로 일을 처리함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a certain individual or group exercises absolute power and handles everything in his/her or its own way.</dd><br>
<dd>2. dictatorship; tyranny</dd><br>
<dd>한 나라의 권력을 한 사람이 모두 차지하고 자기 마음대로 하는 정치.</dd><br>
<dd>A form of politics in which a single person exercises absolute power and handles everything in his/her own way in a country.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>